import React from 'react'
import { Avatar, ListItem, ListItemIcon, ListItemText,Box } from '@material-ui/core'

const Instructions = ({instruction}) => {
    return (
        <Box>
            
            
            <ListItem>
                <ListItemIcon>
                    <Avatar>
                        {instruction.number}
                    </Avatar>
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText primary={instruction.step} />
            </ListItem>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default Instructions
